                            <comment id="13562922" author="alangates" created="Fri, 25 Jan 2013 19:16:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes to the code look fine, but we definitely need a unit test to check that they work.  Adding it in TestGrunt as Rohini suggested makes sense.  Canceling the patch pending adding of tests.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
